LOVE
Love.
love.
There are all different types of love.
Motherly love,
Fatherly love,
Brotherly love,
Sisterly love,
Passionate love.
Love.
Love is like a burning flame,
It lights up your life,
It burns uncontrollably,
The flame flickers,
Like a flicker tears.
Not tears on pain,
Not tears of hate,
Not tears of sadness,
Not tears of happiness,
But tears of love.
love.
All different types of love.
Passionate love,
Sisterly love,
Brotherly love,
Fatherly love,
Motherly love.
Love.
You have to love yourself,
Before you can love others.
Love.

